4072px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;\">{#16}Таътилга чиқувчи ходим ишлайдиган бўлим <span class=\"leading\"></span>номи </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt; font-weight: bold;\"> </span></p>\n</td>\n<td 4=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 41.883656509695px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-17\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;\">{#17}Ходимнинг лавозими</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt; font-weight: bold;\"> </span></p>\n</td>\n<td 4=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 38.559556786704px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;\">{#18}Ходимнинг Ф.И.О</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n</td>\n<td 4=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 25.927977839335px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-19\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;\">{#19}Меҳнат таътилига чиқувчи ходимнинг табел рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt; font-weight: bold;\"> </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n</td>\n<td 4=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 31.91135734072px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-20\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;\">{#20}Ходимнинг таътил кунлари муддати </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n</td>\n<td 4=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 48.531855955679px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-21\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;\">{#21}меҳнат таътили учун асос бўлувчи йилнинг бошлан